text: is a Japanese taekwondo competitor. Competing in the 49 kg category she won a bronze medal at the 2018 Asian Games and placed fifth in 2014. Her elder brother Yuma Yamada won a bronze medal in taekwondo at the 2014 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female taekwondo practitioners Category:Asian Games medalists in taekwondo Category:Taekwondo practitioners at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Japan Category:Taekwondo practitioners at the 2018 Asian Games
